{
    "Description": "<h3>Usage</h3><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\">s:trimRWS()\n</pre><ul><li><code><strong>s</strong></code>: The string to trim.</li></ul><p>Returns a new string with all trailing (right-end) whitespace removed. Leading whitespace and internal spacing are preserved.</p><h4><br></h4><h3>Notes</h3><ul><li>Only trailing whitespace is removed; whitespace at the beginning or within the string is unaffected.</li><li>This function is equivalent to: <code><a href=\"@string:gsub\" target=\"_blank\">string:gsub</a>(s, '%s+$', '')</code></li></ul><p><br></p><h3>Returns</h3><ul><li>A new string with trailing whitespace removed. <em><u>(string)</u></em></li></ul><p><br></p><h3>Example</h3><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\">local S = 'Trim me.&nbsp; &nbsp;'\nlocal T = S:trimRWS()&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;-- T is now \"Trim me.\"\n</pre>",
    "Name": "string:trimRWS",
    "Parameters": null,
    "ParameterTable": false,
    "SummaryLine": "Trims whitespace from the right (end) of a string."
}